quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  14,43,"Iwo adzathamanga kupita kutsogolo, makosi osololoka, mitu yokwezedwa ndi maso awo otuzuka ndipo mitima yawo idzakhala yopanda chilichonse"
  14,44,"Achenjeze anthu za tsiku limene chilango chidzadza pa iwo ndipo anthu ochita zoipa adzati, “Ambuye wathu tipatseni mpumulo wa kanthawi kochepa ndipo ife tidzamvera kuitana kwanu ndi kutsatira Atumwi anu.” Koma adzati kwa iwo, “Kodi inu nthawi zina simudalumbira kuti simudzafa?”"
  14,45,Inu mumakhala m’nyumba za anthu amene adachimwira miyoyo yawo pamene mumadziwa zonse zimene tidawachitira iwo. Ndipo Ife tidakuikirani chitsanzo
  14,46,"Ndithudi iwo akonza chiwembu chawo ndipo chiwembu chawo chili ndi Mulungu ngakhale kuti chiwembu chawo chinali choti, chingathe kuchotsa mapiri"
  14,47,Musaganize kuti Mulungu adzalephera kukwaniritsa lonjezo lake limene adapereka kwa Atumwi ake. Ndithudi Mulungu ali ndi mphamvu ndipo amatha kulanga
  14,48,"Pa tsiku limene dziko lapansi lidzasinthidwa kukhala dziko lapansi la mtundu wina, ndi kumwamba kukhala kwa tsopano, mtundu onse udzaonekera pamaso pa Mulungu, Mmodzi yekha yemwe ndi Mwini mphamvu zonse"
  14,49,Pa tsiku limeneli iwe udzaona anthu osakhulupirira atamangidwa m’magoli
  14,50,Zovala zawo zidzakhala zakuda ngati phula ndi nkhope zawo zidzakutidwa ndi malawi a moto
  14,51,Kuti Mulungu alipire munthu aliyense pa zimene adachita. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wachangu powerengera
  14,52,Uwu ndi uthenga kwa anthu onse kuti achenjezedwe nawo ndi kudziwa kuti Mulungu ndi mmodzi yekha ndi kuti anthu anzeru akumbukire